                                "byte_start": 91794,
                                "byte_stop": 141636,
                                "text": "The opnions of the Court in No. 85-993, Hobbie versus Unemployment Appeals Commission of Florida, No. 85-999 United States against Paradise will be announced by Justice Brennan."
